tika.dc.description: Ms. Rosenshein provides a hands-on approach for helping you and your highly sensitive child. In Parenting the Highly Sensitive Child you will find solutions that work and are easy to apply to home life, school life and your childs emotional world. You will also learn:What a highly sensitive child is and how it ties into ADHDThe 4 types of sensitive childrenTips & Tools for helping your sensitive child make it in a less than sensitive world
